data.description: This Absolutely Stunning Home in The Highly Desired Lakes at PGA Village is A Masterpiece. Sitting right on the Golf Course this Home Has Two Master Bedrooms Fit For Royalty along with a Third Bedroom and Private Office/ Trophy Room. You will be Delighted to walk into this Home and Explore the Open Dine-In Kitchen with your own Side Patio and Sliding Glass. Enormous Living Room with High Ceilings Throughout, Flowing right out to The Screened in Patio and your Own Personal Sanctuary.Stone Finished Pool Area with Calm Ripples of the Waterfalls. Don't miss your Shot to live The Champions Way. Newer A/C, water Heater and pool pump. Call to set up a Showing.This Home is Ready for your Personal Touch and the Perfect layout for the creative mind to make their own. Priced well below Market Value
